{"domain":"GitHub community","question":"A company wants to use open-source style collaboration internally. What is this called?","options":["InnerSource","GitHub Sponsors","Public repository","Starred repositories list"],"answer":"InnerSource","explanation":"InnerSource applies open-source principles inside an organization."},
